 Wales.</ref> || xx(x)Cn<ref group=nb name=ACT/> || VK1xx<ref group=nb name=ACT/>\n| ACT\n| 02nn,<ref group=nb name=PO&c>This is used for some PO box and large users only.</ref> 26nn, 29nn || +61 2 62xx xxxx<br/>+61 2 61xx xxxx || +10 || +11\n|-\n| New South Wales\n| NSW\n| 2xx(x) || xx(x)Nn || VK2xx\n| NSW\n| 1nnn,<ref group=nb name=PO&c/> 2nnn || {{nowrap|+61 2 xxxx xxxx}}<ref group=nb name=exceptions>Some exceptions apply to numbers in this state's [[Telephone numbers in Australia#Geographic numbers|number range]].</ref> || +10 (+{{frac|9|1|2}})<ref group=nb name=NSWTime>The state of New South Wales observes Australian Eastern Standard Time except for [[Broken Hill]] and the surrounding region, which observes Australian Central Standard Time.</ref>|| +11\n|-\n| Victoria\n| Vic\n| 3xx(x) || xx(x)Vn || VK3xx\n| VIC\n| 3nnn, 8nnn<ref group=nb name=PO&c/> || +61 3 xxxx xxxx<ref group=nb name=exceptions/> || +10 || +11\n|-\n| Queensland\n| Qld\n| 4xx(x) || xx(x)Qn || VK4xx\n| QLD\n| 4nnn, 9nnn<ref group=nb name=PO&c/> || +61 7 xxxx xxxx ||colspan=\"2\"| +10\n|-\n| South Australia\n| SA\n| 5xx(x) || xx(x)Sn || VK5xx\n| SA\n| 5nnn || +61 8 8xxx xxxx<br/>+61 8 7xxx xxxx || +{{frac|9|1|2}} || +{{frac|10|1|2}}\n|-\n| Western Australia\n| WA\n| 6xx(x) || xx(x)Wn || VK6xx\n| WA\n| 6nnn || +61 8 9xxx xxxx<br/>+61 8 6xxx xxxx ||colspan=\"2\"| +8\n|-\n| Tasmania\n| Tas\n| 7xx(x) || xx(x)Tn || VK7xx\n| TAS\n| 7nnn || +61 3 6xxx xxxx || +10 || +11\n|-\n| Northern Territory\n| NT\n| 8xx(x) || xx(x)Dn || VK8xx\n| NT\n| 08nn || +61 8 89xx xxxx ||colspan=\"2\"| +{{frac|9|1|2}}\n|-\n!colspan=\"10\"| External territories\n|-\n| Norfolk Island\n|\n| 2xx(x) || xx(x)Nn || VK2xx\n| NSW\n| 2899 || +672 3 xx xxx ||colspan=\"2\"| +11\n|-\n| Christmas Island\n|\n| 6xx(x) || xx(x)Wn || VK9xx\n| WA\n| 6798 || +61 8 9164 xxxx ||colspan=\"2\"| +7\n|-\n| Cocos Island\n|\n| 6xx(x) || xx(x)Wn || VK9xx\n| WA\n| 6799 || +61 8 9162 xxxx ||colspan=\"2\"| +{{frac|6|1|2}}\n|-\n| Australian Antarctic Territ